{"tid":2501299,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"單日31萬確診 印度大缺氧  高院︰偷呃拐騙都要確保供應","createTime":"2021-04-23T09:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:26:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"900e497f89e8fc0410d2a72e3e773bee7b28fa44","tid":2501299,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210422/DBOKLX62XBET5DDV6DBBHHWVSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FDBOKLX62XBET5DDV6DBBHHWVSM%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzqF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=7f82042b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FDBOKLX62XBET5DDV6DBBHHWVSM%2F&h=b914bac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210422/DBOKLX62XBET5DDV6DBBHHWVSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n單日31萬確診 印度大缺氧 <br />\n高院︰偷呃拐騙都要確保供應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NdyrWWXm2AWhZN0z8mfYWD4wZuE=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MT3MNTKYVZG63NIAFAXNW6EG24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNdyrWWXm2AWhZN0z8mfYWD4wZuE%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMT3MNTKYVZG63NIAFAXNW6EG24.jpg&h=0d924a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在新德里的火葬場，親屬向染疫亡者作最後道別。<br />\n<br />\n【物資匱乏】印度COVID-19疫情失控，昨天確診近31.5萬宗，創下全球單日確診最高紀錄，如潮般的入院者壓垮當地醫療系統，其中重症病人賴以續命的氧氣更是嚴重短缺，有家屬在社交網站請求外界施援，高等法院下令新德里「哪管是乞求、賒借或偷呃拐騙，都要確保氧氣供應無虞」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：東奧傳聖火首現確診 警員染疫<br />\n<br />\n號稱醫藥用品生產大國的印度，在今次疫情大爆發中不堪一擊，病床、藥物、呼吸機及氧氣統統匱乏。住在德里南部的英語教師喬杜里發現一對70多歲染疫鄰居病情日益嚴重，在Whatsapp群組呼籲說：「緊急求救。鄰居夫婦情況很差，他們需要氧氣，但找不到。請幫忙。」<br />\n<br />\n如此援助在小城市更難尋求。住在印北的蒂瓦里東奔西跑，找了逾10家醫院才為日益虛弱的病父找到一張床位，以為有救，院方翌日卻告之氧氣快用完，他們必須轉院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i4ybS1wmH6mDmZSyHPnC8LWMIik=/510x335/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5JR2PQGR7NATJKMYHHA6FISNGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi4ybS1wmH6mDmZSyHPnC8LWMIik%3D%2F510x335%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5JR2PQGR7NATJKMYHHA6FISNGY.jpg&h=b98d6d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■班加羅爾一間氧氣廠的工人正趕工為壓縮氧氣樽充氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞德西韋炒至萬元一劑<br />\n<br />\n「朋友不知用了甚麼方法，弄來了一小樽氧氣，我便載着父親周圍再找病床，當時在後座吸着氧氣的他很焦慮，我一直安慰，給他希望，但他最終在車內過世。」蒂瓦里怒斥：「這是制度和領袖的失敗！」<br />\n<br />\n蒂瓦里的悲慘遭遇不是個別例子，印東居民旁遮的母親中招入院後，病情持續嚴重，他千辛萬苦從一位剛病逝的遠房親戚那邊，找來一些瑞德西韋，這些抗病毒藥物目前每劑在印度已炒至1,340美元（約一萬港元），比平常高出30倍。<br />\n<br />\n可是，旁遮不久也遇上蒂瓦里的難題：醫院缺氧，導致病母情況轉趨危殆，他說：「幸好我們幾小時後以極高昂的價錢，及時把她轉到一間私家醫院。」全印度幾乎所有氧氣廠外都有捧着氣樽等待「打氣」的人龍，醫療用氧黑市價已炒至正常九倍，但仍一樽難求。<br />\n<br />\n印度官方對疫情掉以輕心，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e49ee3_wbnwnzbkIyuRBACW2dXw=/510x344/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6FOM6CIXYVEOLBBGBMBRHQQA2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe49ee3_wbnwnzbkIyuRBACW2dXw%3D%2F510x344%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6FOM6CIXYVEOLBBGBMBRHQQA2I.jpg&h=40f9d754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■得悉丈夫染疫身亡，婦人悲慟不已；印度超過18.5萬人死於COVID-19。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下令用工業氧氣應急<br />\n<br />\n政府抗疫失敗，新德里高等法院除了怒斥荒謬，更下令當局用規格較低的工業氧氣頂替，總之救人要緊。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/英國《衞報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JMNr7w3dajTjBMHRNVD6F1A9I0s=/510x1096/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNDVER4LZ5HMVMVFTLH6EXXL5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJMNr7w3dajTjBMHRNVD6F1A9I0s%3D%2F510x1096%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNDVER4LZ5HMVMVFTLH6EXXL5U.jpg&h=ecc696b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d537ca50c5d82a05cab007ae1a166e0336092d2","tid":2501299,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4356c07b77ae55e89c112f08bb7bd7cd9c861e24","tid":2501299,"uid":49784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"清潔消毒左d 餐具先開飯會唔會實際d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b87864dd09ad6b2e9646b89ec078852c29f02a","tid":2501299,"uid":38982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"印度應該強制確診者去恒河游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5639b7f5b1e527320a2387a7ffa67c07608f96aa","tid":2501299,"uid":164770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"睇外國好多國家爆得好勁，肺炎應該好快又翻香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b767c47d5373de4d12a7b16f74a129875bdddcfb","tid":2501299,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"攻打支那啦"},{"pid":"8144539c3e984f2cf0d10457fd499b31bbb3337c","tid":2501299,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"仲好，好快可以群體免疫"},{"pid":"e2197efdb49ec89c993fe4837132b4d88ff6d686","tid":2501299,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:21:01.000Z","msg":"仲唔打鳩支那泄憤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45737f30e6d47a7e4cf59d7100c1f729661e5882","tid":2501299,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:21:32.000Z","msg":"瑞德西韋 係咪即係 輝瑞/BioNTech ？"},{"pid":"31babee793d7de8ca31dc603fa7a9c98d32c2657","tid":2501299,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":